org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.selection

Class SelectionManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ow2.proactive.resourcemanager.selection.SelectionManager
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ProbablisticSelectionManager

    public abstract class SelectionManager
extends Object
    An interface of selection manager which is responsible for nodes selection from a pool of free nodes for further scripts execution.
